Lisa Nicole Carson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_Nicole_Carson 0 Lisa Nicole Carson (born July 12, 1969) is an American actress. She is known for her work on U.S. television, including supporting roles in NBC's ER and Fox's Ally McBeal. Carson appeared in the roles simultaneously, but afterwards, she withdrew from acting until 2012 when she appeared in the final episode of David E. Kelley's Harry's Law.
